<li>We were so saddened to hear of your loss.  May your memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and love as you navigate this profound sorrow.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and your family with heartfelt sympathy.</li>
<li>May the love surrounding you ease your pain.</li>
<li>With deepest sympathy, we mourn the loss of your [relationship to deceased].</li>
